{
  "stem": "3449.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were doing bricks-- making bricks and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and they had, I don't know, about 30 Germans with a cook.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, a regular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were staying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they heard that they are not bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That they're looking for workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They don't care who they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, and it didn't make sense, but it made-- somehow it worked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were Jews working there, and this guy was not bad at all-- the guy that ran the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father found out about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got a hold of a Ukrainian or Polish man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forget now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He'll pay him and all that, for the food and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were like friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to deal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if something happens in the city, if the liquidation comes in, if we have a chance to run away, he'll send me, my sister, and my mother over until the liquidation's over.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we look further for a place to hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we waited until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my aunt came over and she says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think this is it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You better run.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
